---
layout: base.njk
title: "AI Glossary | Key Terms & Definitions | Zunkiree Labs"
description: "Comprehensive AI glossary explaining RAG, LLMs, vector databases, embeddings, and 20+ key artificial intelligence terms. Clear definitions for business leaders."
permalink: /glossary/
---

{# =====================================================
   HERO SECTION
   ===================================================== #}
<section class="pt-20 md:pt-28 pb-12 md:pb-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    {# Breadcrumb #}
    <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm mb-8" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="text-zunkiree-600 hover:underline">Home</a>
      <span class="text-warm-400">/</span>
      <span class="text-warm-600">Glossary</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-zunkiree-600 font-medium mb-4">AI Glossary</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-[56px] font-normal tracking-tight leading-[1.1] text-gray-900 mb-6">
        AI terms explained
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Clear, practical definitions of artificial intelligence concepts. From RAG and LLMs to embeddings and vector databases—understand the technology powering modern AI systems.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# =====================================================
   CATEGORY FILTER
   ===================================================== #}
<section class="py-8 bg-gray-50 border-y border-gray-200 sticky top-16 z-30">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2" x-data="{ filter: 'all' }">
      <button @click="filter = 'all'" :class="filter === 'all' ? 'bg-zunkiree-600 text-white' : 'bg-white text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100'" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium border border-gray-200 transition-colors">
        All Terms
      </button>
      {% set categories = [] %}
      {% for term in glossary %}
        {% if term.category not in categories %}
          {% set categories = (categories.push(term.category), categories) %}
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
      {% for category in categories | sort %}
      <button @click="filter = '{{ category | lower | replace(' ', '-') }}'" :class="filter === '{{ category | lower | replace(' ', '-') }}' ? 'bg-zunkiree-600 text-white' : 'bg-white text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100'" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium border border-gray-200 transition-colors">
        {{ category }}
      </button>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# =====================================================
   TERMS GRID
   ===================================================== #}
<section class="py-12 md:py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6" x-data="{ filter: 'all' }">
      {% for term in glossary | sort(attribute='term') %}
      <a href="/glossary/{{ term.id }}/" class="group block border border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-zunkiree-400 hover:shadow-lg transition-all" x-show="filter === 'all' || filter === '{{ term.category | lower | replace(' ', '-') }}'">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-zunkiree-600 font-medium mb-2">{{ term.category }}</p>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 group-hover:text-zunkiree-600 transition-colors mb-3">
          {{ term.term }}
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          {{ term.shortDef }}
        </p>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# =====================================================
   CTA SECTION
   ===================================================== #}
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal text-gray-900 mb-4">
      Ready to implement AI?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Our team can help you turn these concepts into real solutions for your business.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/services/ai-development/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-zunkiree-600 text-white font-medium hover:bg-zunkiree-700 transition-colors" data-track="cta" data-cta-id="glossary-services">
        Explore AI Services
      </a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-900 text-gray-900 font-medium hover:bg-gray-900 hover:text-white transition-colors" data-track="cta" data-cta-id="glossary-contact">
        Talk to an Expert
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
